Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell Kin'emon-{\i1}kun{\i0} and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That we'll fight along with you at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon... {\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you two, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's getting busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tons of people\Nwho won't last the week before the great battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you'll excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're pretty exhausted, officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll repeat myself over and over again\Nuntil you believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the great thief Ushimitsu Kozo\Nwho created turmoil in the Flower Capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up! If you're really him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you appear around midnight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh! You're taking me for a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get out of here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. No wonder we did not notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Shaking the Nation!\NThe Identity of Ushimitsu Kozo The Chivalrous Thief!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Big news! Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The great thief Ushimitsu Kozo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,FLOWER CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...who caused trouble \Nin the Flower Capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...finally got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His number is finally up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Special report! Special report!\NThere's big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushimitsu Kozo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0},\Nthere is something that I want you to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Ushimitsu Kozo\Nwho we caught yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,None of you can understand the pain of\Nlosing a beloved woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,About the Oiran, Komurasaki's death,\Nmy sympathies are with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But with all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoshiro's move was wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If he let someone\Nwho stood against you walk away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it would have undermined\Nyour authority and reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not care about Ushimitsu Kozo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other woman as beautiful as Komurasaki\Nin the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so great to see you, Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushimitsu Kozo was not \Njust another petty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushimitsu Kozo, the cowardly burglar\Nwho caused trouble in the Flower Capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a hero-wannabe, small-time \Ncrook who gives away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the money and goods he steals to poor people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We are holding him at the Prisoners' Quarters\Nin Rasetsu Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but the truth is his identity is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He is... alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... I cannot believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are from the Kurozumi Family.\NWhy didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He is... He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord! Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do about Ushimitsu Kozo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Execute him! And show it to public\Nto set an example!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Illuminate the Light-Scrolls across the Land of Wano\Nimmediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light-Scrolls are already prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, Komurasaki's funeral will be held\Nin the Flower Capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We are expecting a crowd of people\Nand it will be chaotic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why we have already prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! This is what we are going to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We will let Ushimitsu Kozo\Nfollow Komurasaki to the grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To accompany her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity to lose the two biggest stars of the capital\Nat the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you could come up \Nwith such a nice idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will witness his execution to the end!\NI need a palanquin now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,EXCAVATION LABOR CAMP, UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making bad jokes\Nso early in the morning, Kaido-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a joke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Word came from the Flower Capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Komurasaki died!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She died!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you think it's a lie,\Nhook up your Light-Scroll Snail!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Komurasaki-{\i1}tan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He found out that Komurasaki died!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that he'll be in \Na bad mood for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble. What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! No time for that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, balloon!\NCan we start today's sumo match already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you idiots gain weight from yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we didn't! It's just your imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--O-Okay.\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--Forget it!\N--Should we tell him that the red-bean soup is all gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Another shock could drive him mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder where the red-bean soup went...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I told Luffy-{\i1}dono \{\i0}Nnot to eat too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating up all the soup in the pot\Nwas too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How can an idiot like him survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just have the sumo match!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! {\i1}Dosukoi{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for dealing with a fool!\NI have to find out the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let me see the Flower Capital now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the Light-Scroll Snail ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light-Scroll Snail has been set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Connect it to the Flower Capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a Video Transponder Snail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That must be the Flower Capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,ATAMAYAMA, KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they are attacking Atamayama!\NScrew them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shutenmaru, this is it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my revenge!\NI'll make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you Atamayama Thieves Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you steal all \Nof my food and weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,THE ATAMAYAMA THIEVES BRIGADE WAS HERE\NSHUTENMARU
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Holdem-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you, Shutenmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll smash you fools to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hysterical! What can you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect stealing food and weapons\Nwould cause this much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Duke-{\i1}sama{\i0}! Kin-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We stole so much.\NFood... And weapons from the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice work. Did you leave the note?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,THE ATAMAYAMA THIEVES BRIGADE WAS HERE\NSHUTENMARU
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we responsible for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of Kin-{\i1}san{\i0}'s plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just the food and the weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--You coward!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your subordinate made such a ruckus in Bakura Town\Nand messed me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...Red Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What are you talking about?!\NI had nothing to do with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you pretending that you don't know?\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just sort it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this Trick Mechanism Sword's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cheap trick won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Then, I'll increase the heat!\NKamijiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that your cheap trick won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me fairly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you noticed yet? Look around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? The fire has \Nspread in all directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I even bother \Nfighting you head-on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to destroy Atamayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Atamayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about Holdem for now!\NLet's retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shutenmaru's hideout has been destroyed!\NThey no longer have a place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of the \NAtamayama Thieves Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late! The fire's spreading too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to extinguish \Nit, Shutenmaru-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Holdem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Bakura Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bakura Town?!\NKaido's army will come after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kick all of their asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't plan for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's notify Duke-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,AN ABANDONED VILLAGE, KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I feel sorry for Ashura Doji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm... But we did it for the greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Bakura Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plan is foiled\Nand we do not know what to do yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But for the time being, we need Ashura to be\Nhostile towards the Animal Kingdom Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we definitely need him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,NORTHERN GRAVEYARD, RINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} and the others\Nhave come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Brook... What's up with you?\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NYou're almost making my eyes pop out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if I had eyes to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you got the wrong idea! Come back in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, okay... If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, how beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but may I see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! He's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry. A curse on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon-{\i1}san{\i0} told me to\Nstay here and say that to people...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...there are so many offerings out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't believe that\Nyou're Momonosuke-{\i1}san{\i0}'s sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as lovely as the Oirans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Because she's an Oiran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be so nice to have someone like her by your side.\NI wish I were you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just sleeping, but she...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I thought you were really cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always make men drool\Nwhenever I sleep alongside them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you like it? Well, I know you loved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're pretty straightforward...\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I wonder where\NNami-{\i1}san{\i0} and the others are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They went to a bathhouse yesterday,\Nso I tried to go meet them, but I couldn't find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, the Flower Capital is\Nin total chaos now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the funeral of Komurasaki-{\i1}san{\i0} the Oiran,\Nthe most beautiful woman in the Land of Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, Ushimitsu Kozo the great thief\Nwho spread the money he stole to the poor got caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's causing a fuss, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushimitsu Kozo got caught?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's written in the broadsheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be executed in the capital today...\NAnd they found out his identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,USHIMITSU KOZO GOT CAUGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's popular in Ebisu Town...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You said Ebisu Town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And his name is, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...Yasu-something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonoyasu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Toko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Toko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving us yesterday!\NWe will not forget your kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't protect her yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I've just come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you came to escort me?\NThat's very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?!\NYour life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Toko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Toko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it will be a lovely day\Nin the Flower Capital today...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The time for Tonoyasu's \Nexecution is approaching.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Straw Hats clear away unassailable guards\Nand rush to stop the execution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will Tonoyasu share the fate of the cherry blossoms?!\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth behind his smile will be revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Straw Hats Run! Save the Captive Tonoyasu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.07,0:23:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
